#Text=( ( WSS ) ) How much campaigning have you done so far ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) I have campaigned in 26 counties across Iowa and also made campaign stops in New Hampshire .
#Text=I have been interviewed on radio shows across the country .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) What are your thoughts on your fellow Republican presidential candidates ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) I think it is a strong field and that the vigorous policy debate underway in the party is good for the country .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Would you ever consider running as a third party or independent candidate ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) I am running as a Republican and am not contemplating a third party or independent candidacy .
#Text=Media blackout

#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Wikinews covered the complaint you filed with the FEC against Fox News in your attempt to be included in the August 6 Debate . In our report , Election Law expert Richard Winger suggested you file a lawsuit rather than an FEC complaint . Do you have an update on your FEC complaint and might you consider filing a lawsuit if you are excluded from future debates ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) We have received notice that the FEC has filed the complaint with Fox News , but nothing else .
#Text=I have written to CNN and the Reagan Foundation requesting inclusion in their September debate .
#Text=At this time I do not expect to file a lawsuit on this matter .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) What is your response to Mr. Winger , who said you had a good case and may have had an opportunity to gain access to the debate if you filed a lawsuit instead of an FEC complaint ?

#Text=( ( Everson ) ) I did look into the possible filing of a law suit and was informed by a prominent election law expert that the chances were quite slim that the courts would intervene in a matter properly before the FEC .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Are you saying that you do not expect to litigate the Fox News matter or do you not expect to file a lawsuit to gain access to future debates ? If so , why ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) I expect to pursue the FOX matter with the FEC .
#Text=I will assess future legal actions as events unfold .

#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Your exclusion from National presidential polls appears to be the biggest detriment to your campaign and effort to appear in debates . Is there anything your campaign can do to include your name in polls to qualify for future debates ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) We have written the polling companies requesting that I be included in the polls .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Have the polling companies responded to your requests ? If so , what have they said ?
#Text=( ( Everson ) ) We have not yet heard from the polling companies .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Are you surprised by your exclusion from presidential polls and events or did you expect this when you announced ?

#Text=( ( Everson ) ) At this still early stage of the race , I am surprised that participation has been limited to established politicians and individuals already enjoying significant name recognition .
#Text=The process should be about surfacing issues of importance to the country and who can best tackle the challenges at hand .
